Package org.dellroad.typetags.example

Annotation Interface PhoneNumber

@Documented @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(TYPE_USE) @TypeTag(restrictTo=java.lang.String.class, validatedBy=Validator.class) public @interface PhoneNumber
Annotates declarations of type String for which the value must be non-null and a valid E.164 phone number.

Optionally, values may be restricted to only allow North American Numbering Plan (NANP) phone numbers.
